Savouring Korea’s street food vibes, one bite at a time at @caffeanno 🇰🇷🍜

PR/AD invite 🤝

If you’re looking to explore korean street food in Birmingham city centre, look no further than Caffe Anno! From pocket friendly prices to adorable interiors, this place has it all. Plus, they’ve got mouthwatering vegetarian options for all the foodies out there! And don’t forget to pair your meals with refreshing bubble teas. 🧋

Lunch with friends in the heart of Birmingham - enjoying a delightful feast of vegetarian Indian street food. Craft beers, great music, and a fantastic vibe added to the charm. From paneer tikka to chhole bhature, and a sweet ending with falooda – it was a culinary adventure! 🍽️🍻🎶 Special thanks to Manager, Dumar for ensuring a fun and comfortable experience at @bundobust .

📍Bundobust, Birmingham
